    "response": "The number of paid holidays varies by province and territory in Canada. However, there are 5 days in the year that are paid holidays in every jurisdiction:\n\n*   New Year’s Day\n*   Good Friday\n*   Canada Day\n*   Labour Day\n*   Christmas Day\n\nEach province and territory may have additional paid holidays.",
